author: AP
title: European Tour events in Morocco, Sweden off amid virus
description: Two more golf events on the European Tour have been called off because of the coronavirus pandemic
content:
VIRGINIA WATER, England (AP) — Two more golf events on the European Tour were called off Monday because of the coronavirus pandemic, ensuring there will be no play until the end of June at the earliest.
